lead_paragraph: CHUNGKING, China, July 1 (AP) -- Japanese troops are overrunning the last few unconquered miles of the railway between Hangshow and Nanchang, against which they began driving from both the East and West six weeks ago, reports from the front said tonight.
abstract: Chinese repel Jap sorties from Tsungfa
